Package Characters.Roles

Class ClanChief

java.lang.Object
Characters.Character
Characters.Roles.ClanChief
public class ClanChief extends Character
Represents a Clan Chief (e.g., Abraracourcix or Caesar). The Chief is responsible for managing a location and its inhabitants. This class provides an interactive menu for the user to give orders.
